  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dad\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d86\u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Japanese professor returns forgotten wallet",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Japanese professor Matrunura Junko's purse was picked up by an airport attendant after it fell on the ground at the Katunayake airport arrival terminal.",
        "The professor who came to Sri Lanka went to the office of a mobile phone company at the airport arrivals terminal to get a mobile phone sim card.",
        "During this transaction, her wallet fell on the floor.",
        "After completing the transaction, the professor had left the airport for the hotel where she was staying and Mrs. PP Swarnalatha, who was engaged in cleaning the airport, had seen this purse, picked it up and immediately handed it over to the airport security personnel.",
        "In that wallet, there was 119,390 Sri Lankan currency, and in it there was also a receipt containing the details that this professor had received a sim card.",
        "The airport security officers contacted the professor and told her to come to the airport and get her wallet.",
        "The Japanese professor who accepted the purse expressed her gratitude by giving prizes to the airport attendant Mrs. PP Swarnalatha and the officials of the airport security department who picked up the purse."
      ],
